{"tid":1827636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈的消費次序","createTime":"2020-01-17T06:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T11:53:11.000Z","uid":272805,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d22ae64a8070719da10dbf80db8caa2f5be75df0","tid":1827636,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈大家都講得好多，咁究竟應該點樣消費，點樣選擇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己嘅簡單原則係咁<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只要佢令到手足有得益，就應該幫襯</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個人消費次序<br />\n平時就 和你Pay / eat 既店舖（小店優先）<br />\n網上（光時，重光號，維基）<br />\n諗唔到（誠哥）<br />\n本土小店<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後，你唔知邊間係黃都好，你一定知道邊一間藍，咁就唔去果間</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人批評黃色經濟圈啲料咪又係大陸來，<br />\n又或者上司係藍，下屬係黃嘅情況<br />\n冇錯， 所以我哋要學識黃中有藍，同藍中有黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n以HKTVMALL 做例子，一樣有藍店喺上面買嘢<br />\n當你買既時候，小部份錢落左維基度，大部分錢去左藍店度，即係黃中藍<br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n假如你去call的士，如果個司機係黃嘅，就算call call台要收返錢，大部份嘅錢都係去左司機嗰度，即係藍中黃<br />\n<br />\n就算係龍門冰室都好，最後都一定會有部份嘅錢會去咗藍色或者紅色資本（利得稅）<br />\n<br />\n我哋要思考嘅係，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點樣可以將黃色資本最大化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家既消費模式又係點？<br />\n不如大家都分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b7dc37925f00964f429988bee9c12750f1868e","tid":1827636,"uid":8732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"和你eat 和你pay 都好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新年3大任務：119大遊行，年廿八和手足團年，各區和你宵，幫手share 比親戚朋友一齊過黃色新年啦<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822470</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A42xLyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA42xLyW.jpg&h=755e56b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45e3f051d4b1075eb67ca694fdcfcda2035b85aa","tid":1827636,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"咁消耗對家本錢算唔算優先?<br />\n齋坐唔俾錢，拎撚晒佢啲免費紙杯，紙巾?"},{"pid":"d4852fb5bc2a4cabb5387c46c26e7df97438b144","tid":1827636,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"幫黑狗叫藍屍外賣"},{"pid":"a9287af2da1b6cb3ead90422465e7d556020f3b7","tid":1827636,"uid":272805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45e3f051d4b1075eb67ca694fdcfcda2035b85aa","tid":1827636,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"咁消耗對家本錢算唔算優先?<br />\n齋坐唔俾錢，拎撚晒佢啲免費紙杯，紙巾?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"絕對算！<br />\n唔係令佢有損失，而係令佢冇收入<br />\n其實即係不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d3a2da63eed09351a8cdc98b93a5f2d74a5d52","tid":1827636,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9287af2da1b6cb3ead90422465e7d556020f3b7","tid":1827636,"uid":272805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45e3f051d4b1075eb67ca694fdcfcda2035b85aa","tid":1827636,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"咁消耗對家本錢算唔算優先?<br />\n齋坐唔俾錢，拎撚晒佢啲免費紙杯，紙巾?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"絕對算！<br />\n唔係令佢有損失，而係令佢冇收入<br />\n其實即係不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"齋坐仲要係咁用佢d免費野唔止無收入，直頭損失啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怕蝕佐時間比佢可以做下鍵盤戰士網上文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444d3f5c9ff58a3eb14339f7678c6ed16021ce5d","tid":1827636,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,